## Constraints

### Use

- Task transition side-effect aynı `$transaction` (Faz 5 handler)
- Task complete → ilgili case transition (workflow command)
- Business days SLA — `BusinessCalendarService` zorunlu
- Delegation: eski DELEGATED + yeni task (update semantic yasak)
- TaskEvent append-only
- DecisionVote unanimity (oy birliği)
- Sessiz kabul: worker cron job (`silent-acceptance.job.ts`); `setInterval` yasak
- SYSTEM actor sessiz kabul transition'da

### Avoid

- Calendar days SLA hesabı
- Delegation as task field update only
- Majority vote instead of unanimity
- setInterval for silent acceptance
- TaskEvent UPDATE/DELETE
- Frontend-only task complete (backend enforcement)

